File: A soccer ball seen next to a net. AFP/Roberto Schmidt  JOHANNESBURG - The Nedbank Cup semi-final fixtures and dates have been confirmed by the PSL. The Limpopo derby featuring TTM and Marumo Gallants will take place on 29 April at the Thohoyandou Stadium. On 30 April, league title contenders Mamelodi Sundowns and Royal AM do battle at Chatsworth in Durban. Tickets for both matches are available at Ticketpro outlets countrywide.